comments.body:
[~tony]/[~viglesias]:

Verified issue is fixed.

*Steps*

# Used admin user of account to create 3 stacks using the following cloudformation template:
{code}
{
  "AWSTemplateFormatVersion" : "2010-09-09",

  "Description" : "Cloudformation Example => Create bucket with public-read access control list (ACL)",

  "Resources" : {
    "S3Bucket" : {
      "Type" : "AWS::S3::Bucket",
      "Properties" : {
        "AccessControl" : "PublicRead"
      },
      "DeletionPolicy" : "Retain"
    }
  },

  "Outputs" : {
      "BucketName": {
          "Value": {
              "Ref": "S3Bucket"
          },
          "Description": "Name of OSG Bucket Created"
      }
  }
}
{code}
{code}
# euform-create-stack --template-file cfn-osg-bucket-template.json BucketStack --region admin-hspencer@group1
arn:aws:cloudformation::617513010345:stack/BucketStack/ee90d309-3a6f-422b-8512-33be9d821423
# euform-create-stack --template-file cfn-osg-bucket-template.json BucketStackV2 --region admin-hspencer@group1
arn:aws:cloudformation::617513010345:stack/BucketStackV2/c792cc23-25bd-4567-801f-86f64197ee9a
# euform-create-stack --template-file cfn-osg-bucket-template.json BucketStackV3 --region admin-hspencer@group1
arn:aws:cloudformation::617513010345:stack/BucketStackV3/fee9c48d-7f8e-4917-8d15-ad6185b8cef3
{code}
# Listed the stacks:
{code}
# euform-describe-stacks --region admin-hspencer@group1
STACK	BucketStack	CREATE_COMPLETE	Complete!	Cloudformation Example => Create bucket with public-read access control list (ACL)	2014-12-22T20:24:33.670Z
OUTPUT	BucketName	bucketstack-s3bucket-ndvsr3sngzbs2
STACK	BucketStackV2	CREATE_COMPLETE	Complete!	Cloudformation Example => Create bucket with public-read access control list (ACL)	2014-12-22T20:24:41.281Z
OUTPUT	BucketName	bucketstackv2-s3bucket-vuddbotvhltoi
STACK	BucketStackV3	CREATE_COMPLETE	Complete!	Cloudformation Example => Create bucket with public-read access control list (ACL)	2014-12-22T20:24:47.120Z
OUTPUT	BucketName	bucketstackv3-s3bucket-wstn7ugzm6al2
{code}

Notice stacks 'BucketStack' and 'BucketStackV3' end with a zero in the milliseconds for date timestamp.
